                <div class="glass-effect border border-indigo-100/30 rounded-lg p-4">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">How long does it take to get a response?</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">We typically respond to all inquiries within 24 hours during business days.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="glass-effect border border-indigo-100/30 rounded-lg p-4">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">Do you offer refunds?</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">Yes, we offer a 30-day money-back guarantee on all our premium plans.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="glass-effect border border-indigo-100/30 rounded-lg p-4">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">How do I report a technical issue?</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">The fastest way to get technical help is to email support@example.com with details about the issue you're experiencing.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>